563ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
564ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
565ret += Top_tag_oldret;
566}
567if((data)->certificate){
568size_t Top_tag_oldret = ret;
569ret = 0;
570ret += der_length_octet_string((data)->certificate);
571ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
572ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
573ret += Top_tag_oldret;
574}
575if((data)->e_text){
576size_t Top_tag_oldret = ret;
577ret = 0;
578ret += der_length_visible_string((data)->e_text);
579ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
580ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
581ret += Top_tag_oldret;
582}
583ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
584return ret;
585}
586
587int ASN1CALL
588copy_Kx509Response(const Kx509Response *from, Kx509Response *to)
589{
590memset(to, 0, sizeof(*to));
591if((from)->error_code) {
592(to)->error_code = malloc(sizeof(*(to)->error_code));
593if((to)->error_code == NULL) goto fail;
594*((to)->error_code) = *((from)->error_code);
595}else
596(to)->error_code = NULL;
597if((from)->hash) {
598(to)->hash = malloc(sizeof(*(to)->hash));
599if((to)->hash == NULL) goto fail;
600if(der_copy_octet_string((from)->hash, (to)->hash)) goto fail;
601}else
602(to)->hash = NULL;
603if((from)->certificate) {
604(to)->certificate = malloc(sizeof(*(to)->certificate));
605if((to)->certificate == NULL) goto fail;
606if(der_copy_octet_string((from)->certificate, (to)->certificate)) goto fail;
607}else
608(to)->certificate = NULL;
609if((from)->e_text) {
610(to)->e_text = malloc(sizeof(*(to)->e_text));
611if((to)->e_text == NULL) goto fail;
612if(der_copy_visible_string((from)->e_text, (to)->e_text)) goto fail;
613}else
614(to)->e_text = NULL;
615return 0;
616fail:
617free_Kx509Response(to);
618return ENOMEM;
619}
